  "texts": [
    "This method also describes the structural semantic information of a part, by training a VAE-based recursive neural network (RvNN) (Socher et al. 2011) with backpropagation through structure (BPTS) (Goller and Küchler 1996).",
    "Therefore at the output of the model, a sketch/view is obtained about the input CAD model.",
    "This paper also utilizes a type of parameter tuning to a great extent, namely the cyclical learning rate (CLR) (Smith 2017).",
    "This approach further requires model optimizations and an implementation of more than one retrieval mode, such as coarse-grained and fine-grained retrievals.",
    "Another well-known 3D data representation format is the voxel grid."
